</ul></nav></section><section class="front-matter"><div class="ameta p font-secondary font-xs">
<hgroup><h1>Refining the retinal phenotype of patients with suspected pentosan polysulfate sodium retinopathy</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Kalaw%20FGP"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Fritz Gerald P Kalaw</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Fritz Gerald P Kalaw</span>, <span class="degrees">MD</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Jacobs Retina Center, University of California San Diego, La Jolla, California, United States of America, 92037</div>
<div class="p">
<sup>2</sup>Shiley Eye Institute, University of California San Diego, La Jolla, California, United States of America, 92037</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Kalaw%20FGP"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Fritz Gerald P Kalaw</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1,</sup><sup>2</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Arias%20JD"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">Juan D Arias</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Juan D Arias</span>, <span class="degrees">BS</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>2</sup>Shiley Eye Institute, University of California San Diego, La Jolla, California, United States of America, 92037</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Arias%20JD"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Juan D Arias</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>2</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Walker%20E"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id3"><span class="name western">Evan Walker</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id3">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Evan Walker</span>, <span class="degrees">MS</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>2</sup>Shiley Eye Institute, University of California San Diego, La Jolla, California, United States of America, 92037</div>
