<sup>2</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Baxter%20SL"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id4"><span class="name western">Sally L Baxter</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id4">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Sally L Baxter</span>, <span class="degrees">MD, MSc</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>2</sup>Shiley Eye Institute, University of California San Diego, La Jolla, California, United States of America, 92037</div>
<div class="p">
